## ⏱️ Complexity Analysis

Let `n` be the size of the array.

### Time Complexity

* Copy array: **O(n)**
* Sort the copied array: **O(n log n)**
* Assign ranks: **O(n)**
* Build the answer: **O(n)**

Overall:

```text id="2lq38j"
O(n log n)
```

### Space Complexity

* Copy of the array: **O(n)**
* Hash map for ranks: **O(n)**

Overall:

```text id="53a87p"
O(n)
```

